    <title>Fifty-eight — LLM Numerial IQ Test</title>
    <link href="https://blog.junyu33.me/en/2026/04/17/llm_numiq/"/>
    <id>https://blog.junyu33.me/en/2026/04/17/llm_numiq/</id>
    <updated>2026-04-16T19:00:00.000Z</updated>
    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Some LLM-oriented IQ evaluations are already available on the Internet. For example, <a href="https://trackingai.org/home">https://trackingai.org/home</a> lists IQ-test results for well-known domestic and international LLMs, including the public Mensa Norway test and a private question set from a Mensa member. However, the Mensa Norway test is largely focused on <strong>visual</strong> reasoning. It may therefore also be useful to understand how LLMs perform on <strong>numerical reasoning</strong>.</p>]]></summary>
