  <entry>
    <title>Fifty-five — Blog 4th anniversary / Talk about the education of last 15 years</title>
    <link href="https://blog.junyu33.me/en/2025/07/06/4th_anni/"/>
    <id>https://blog.junyu33.me/en/2025/07/06/4th_anni/</id>
    <updated>2025-07-06T15:30:00.000Z</updated>
    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>My blog turns four this year, and this year also marks my graduation from undergraduate studies. Therefore, the theme of this anniversary is to reflect on the domestic education that has accompanied me for the past fifteen years.</p>
<p>This is a heavy topic, but I don't intend to delve into lengthy discussions. Instead, I've chosen a lighter approach: by evaluating the teachers I've encountered from elementary school to university, I hope to sketch a rough outline of education from my perspective.</p>]]></summary>
